nodes.text: Murra Mors was the wife of Moff Delian Mors. Four years prior to the skirmish that Moff Mors had with the Free Ryloth Movement on Ryloth, Murra had died in a transport accident on Coruscant. This left the Moff feeling purposeless and led her to neglect her duties in the years leading to the skirmish with the Free Ryloth movement.
